    "NOS <span class=\"text-primary\">04</span><br> DIVISIONS": "OUR <span class=\"text-primary\">04</span><br> DIVISIONS",
    "AIAE STRUCTURE SON DÉVELOPPEMENT AUTOUR DE<br> <span class=\"font-heavy\">QUATRE DIVISIONS COMPLÉMENTAIRES</span>, ENSEMBLE,<br> ELLES FORMENT UN <span class=\"font-heavy\">ÉCOSYSTÈME INÉDIT SUR LE</span><br> <span class=\"font-heavy\">MARCHÉ OUEST-AFRICAIN.</span>": "AIAE STRUCTURES ITS DEVELOPMENT AROUND<br> <span class=\"font-heavy\">FOUR COMPLEMENTARY DIVISIONS</span>, TOGETHER,<br> THEY FORM AN <span class=\"font-heavy\">UNPRECEDENTED ECOSYSTEM IN THE</span><br> <span class=\"font-heavy\">WEST AFRICAN MARKET.</span>",
