    "CONSTRUCTION": "CONSTRUCTION",
    "<span class=\"font-heavy text-gray-900\">Notre cœur de métier.</span> Nous concevons et<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> réalisons des <span class=\"font-heavy text-gray-900\">infrastructures durables</span> : villas<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> résidentielles, bâtiments commerciaux, ouvrages<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> d’art et infrastructures techniques. <span class=\"font-heavy text-primary\">Conception<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> architecturale et structurelle.</span> <span class=\"font-heavy text-gray-900\">Construction tous<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> standings (Standard à Prestige). Ouvrages<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> d’art</span> <span class=\"font-heavy text-primary\">(ponts, murs de soutènement, etc.)</span>.<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> <span class=\"font-heavy text-primary\">Réhabilitation et extension</span> <span class=\"font-heavy text-gray-900\">de bâtiments<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> existants.</span>": "<span class=\"font-heavy text-gray-900\">Our core business.</span> We design and<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> build <span class=\"font-heavy text-gray-900\">sustainable infrastructures</span>: residential<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> villas, commercial buildings, engineering<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> structures and technical infrastructures. <span class=\"font-heavy text-primary\">Architectural and<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> structural design.</span> <span class=\"font-heavy text-gray-900\">Construction for all<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> standards (Standard to Prestige). Engineering<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> structures</span> <span class=\"font-heavy text-primary\">(bridges, retaining walls, etc.)</span>.<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> <span class=\"font-heavy text-primary\">Rehabilitation and extension</span> <span class=\"font-heavy text-gray-900\">of existing<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> buildings.</span>",
    "À partir de <span class=\"font-black text-lg md:text-xl\">330 000 FCFA/m²</span>": "From <span class=\"font-black text-lg md:text-xl\">330,000 FCFA/sqm</span>",
    "ÉNERGIE": "ENERGY",
    "Solutions <span class=\"font-heavy text-gray-900\">d’autonomie énergétique</span> pour vos<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> installations. Nous dimensionnons et installons des<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> <span class=\"font-heavy text-gray-900\">systèmes solaires adaptés aux besoins des entreprises<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> et exploitations agricoles</span>. <span class=\"font-heavy text-secondary\">Solaire C&I</span> (commercial et<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> industriel) pour entreprises et exploitations. <span class=\"font-heavy text-secondary\">Systèmes<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> hybrides</span> avec stockage par batteries. Solutions pour<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> <span class=\"font-heavy text-secondary\">sites isolés</span> ou <span class=\"font-heavy text-secondary\">sans raccordement</span>. <span class=\"font-heavy text-secondary\">Maintenance et<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> optimisation</span> des installations": "Solutions for <span class=\"font-heavy text-gray-900\">energy autonomy</span> for your<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> facilities. We dimension and install<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> <span class=\"font-heavy text-gray-900\">solar systems tailored to the needs of businesses<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> and farms</span>. <span class=\"font-heavy text-secondary\">C&I Solar</span> (commercial and<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> industrial) for businesses and farms. <span class=\"font-heavy text-secondary\">Hybrid<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> systems</span> with battery storage. Solutions for<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> <span class=\"font-heavy text-secondary\">isolated sites</span> or <span class=\"font-heavy text-secondary\">off-grid locations</span>. <span class=\"font-heavy text-secondary\">Maintenance and<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> optimization</span> of installations",
    "Lancement <span class=\"font-black text-[18px] md:text-2xl\">2026</span>": "Launch in <span class=\"font-black text-[18px] md:text-2xl\">2026</span>",
    "SÉCURITÉ": "SECURITY",
    "<span class=\"font-heavy text-gray-900\">Protection haute performance</span> pour vos biens et vos<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> personnes. Nous concevons et installons <span class=\"font-heavy text-gray-900\">des solutions<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> de sécurité physique</span> répondant aux <span class=\"font-heavy text-gray-900\">normes<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> européennes (EN 1143-1)</span>. <span class=\"font-heavy text-primary\">Chambres fortes</span> et <span class=\"font-heavy text-primary\">coffres<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> certifiés</span> (banques, entreprises). <span class=\"font-heavy text-primary\">Safe rooms</span>, <span class=\"font-heavy text-primary\">salles de<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> repli sécurisées</span> pour particuliers ou dirigeants.<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> <span class=\"font-heavy text-primary\">Armureries</span> et <span class=\"font-heavy text-primary\">locaux de stockage sensible.</span> Systèmes<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> de <span class=\"font-heavy text-primary\">contrôle d’accès</span>": "<span class=\"font-heavy text-gray-900\">High-performance protection</span> for your assets and<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> people. We design and install <span class=\"font-heavy text-gray-900\">solutions<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> for physical security</span> complying with <span class=\"font-heavy text-gray-900\">European<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> standards (EN 1143-1)</span>. <span class=\"font-heavy text-primary\">Strong rooms</span> and <span class=\"font-heavy text-primary\">certified<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> safes</span> (banks, businesses). <span class=\"font-heavy text-primary\">Safe rooms</span>, <span class=\"font-heavy text-primary\">secure<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> retreat rooms</span> for individuals or executives.<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> <span class=\"font-heavy text-primary\">Armories</span> and <span class=\"font-heavy text-primary\">sensitive storage rooms.</span> Systems<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> for <span class=\"font-heavy text-primary\">access control</span>",
    "Prochainement": "Coming soon",
    "PRÉFABRICATION": "PREFABRICATION",
    "Production industrielle d’éléments de construction pour<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> <span class=\"font-heavy text-gray-900\">des chantiers plus rapides, plus économiques<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> (-15 à -25% sur les coûts)</span> et de <span class=\"font-heavy text-gray-900\">meilleure qualité.</span> <span class=\"font-heavy text-secondary\">BTC</span><br class=\"hidden md:block\"> (briques de terre compressée), <span class=\"font-heavy text-secondary\">matériau écologique</span><br class=\"hidden md:block\"> local. Éléments en <span class=\"font-heavy text-secondary\">béton précontraint</span> (portées longues,<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> résistance accrue). <span class=\"font-heavy text-secondary\">Nervures</span> et <span class=\"font-heavy text-secondary\">poutrelles</span> pour<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> planchers. Éléments pour <span class=\"font-heavy text-secondary\">ponts</span> et <span class=\"font-heavy text-secondary\">ouvrages d’art</span>": "Industrial production of construction elements for<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> <span class=\"font-heavy text-gray-900\">faster, more economical projects<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> (-15 to -25% on costs)</span> and <span class=\"font-heavy text-gray-900\">better quality.</span> <span class=\"font-heavy text-secondary\">CEB</span><br class=\"hidden md:block\"> (compressed earth blocks), <span class=\"font-heavy text-secondary\">ecological material</span><br class=\"hidden md:block\"> local. Elements in <span class=\"font-heavy text-secondary\">prestressed concrete</span> (long spans,<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> increased resistance). <span class=\"font-heavy text-secondary\">Ribs</span> and <span class=\"font-heavy text-secondary\">joists</span> for<br class=\"hidden md:block\"> floors. Elements for <span class=\"font-heavy text-secondary\">bridges</span> and <span class=\"font-heavy text-secondary\">engineering structures</span>",
    "Pourquoi<br> Choisir AIAE ?": "Why<br> Choose AIAE?",
    "UN INTERLOCUTEUR UNIQUE": "A SINGLE POINT OF CONTACT",
    "Fini la coordination entre architecte, bureau<br class=\"hidden xl:block\"> d’études, constructeur et installateurs. <span class=\"font-heavy\">AIAE<br class=\"hidden xl:block\"> prend en charge l’intégralité de votre projet</span>,<br class=\"hidden xl:block\"> de la première esquisse à la remise des clés.": "No more coordination between architect, design<br class=\"hidden xl:block\"> office, builder and installers. <span class=\"font-heavy\">AIAE<br class=\"hidden xl:block\"> takes charge of your entire project</span>,<br class=\"hidden xl:block\"> from the first sketch to the key handover.",
    "EXPERTISE TECHNIQUE AVANCÉE": "ADVANCED TECHNICAL EXPERTISE",
    "<span class=\"font-heavy\">Forte de plus de 18 ans d’expérience en génie<br class=\"hidden xl:block\"> civil</span>, AIAE dispose de <span class=\"font-heavy\">compétences rares pour<br class=\"hidden xl:block\"> traiter des projets complexes</span> : ouvrages d’art,<br class=\"hidden xl:block\"> béton précontraint, structures spéciales.": "<span class=\"font-heavy\">With over 18 years of experience in civil<br class=\"hidden xl:block\"> engineering</span>, AIAE possesses <span class=\"font-heavy\">rare skills to<br class=\"hidden xl:block\"> handle complex projects</span>: engineering structures,<br class=\"hidden xl:block\"> prestressed concrete, special structures.",
    "DES ENGAGEMENTS TENUS": "COMMITMENTS KEPT",
    "Dans un secteur où la parole ne vaut souvent<br class=\"hidden xl:block\"> rien, <span class=\"font-heavy\">nous faisons de la fiabilité notre marque<br class=\"hidden xl:block\"> de fabrique.</span> Délais respectés, budgets<br class=\"hidden xl:block\"> maîtrisés, qualité garantie.": "In a sector where words are often worth<br class=\"hidden xl:block\"> nothing, <span class=\"font-heavy\">we make reliability our trademark.<br class=\"hidden xl:block\"> </span> Deadlines met, budgets<br class=\"hidden xl:block\"> controlled, quality guaranteed.",
    "TRANSPARENCE TOTALE": "TOTAL TRANSPARENCY",
    "<span class=\"font-heavy\">Devis détaillés basés sur notre Bordereau<br class=\"hidden xl:block\"> des Prix Unitaires (BPU)</span>, suivi de chantier<br class=\"hidden xl:block\"> accessible, facturation claire. <span class=\"font-heavy\">Vous savez<br class=\"hidden xl:block\"> exactement ce que vous payez et pourquoi.</span>": "<span class=\"font-heavy\">Detailed quotes based on our Unit Price<br class=\"hidden xl:block\"> Schedule (BPU)</span>, accessible site<br class=\"hidden xl:block\"> monitoring, clear billing. <span class=\"font-heavy\">You know<br class=\"hidden xl:block\"> exactly what you are paying for and why.</span>",
    "SOLUTIONS INTÉGRÉES UNIQUES": "UNIQUE INTEGRATED SOLUTIONS",
    "Construction + Énergie + Sécurité : <span class=\"font-heavy\">nous<br class=\"hidden xl:block\"> pouvons livrer un bâtiment autonome en<br class=\"hidden xl:block\"> énergie et sécurisé dès la conception.</span> Une<br class=\"hidden xl:block\"> combinaison rare sur le marché togolais.": "Construction + Energy + Security: <span class=\"font-heavy\">we<br class=\"hidden xl:block\"> can deliver an autonomous building in<br class=\"hidden xl:block\"> energy and secured from conception.</span> A<br class=\"hidden xl:block\"> rare combination in the Togolese market.",
