    "DEVIS GRATUIT DÉTAILLÉ": "DETAILED FREE QUOTE",
    "Vous recevez un <span class=\"font-heavy\">devis ligne par<br class=\"hidden xl:block\"> ligne, basé sur notre BPU</span>. Pas de<br class=\"hidden xl:block\"> mauvaises surprises.": "You receive a <span class=\"font-heavy\">line-by-line quote,<br class=\"hidden xl:block\"> based on our Unit Price Schedule</span>. No<br class=\"hidden xl:block\"> bad surprises.",
    "PLANNING CONTRACTUEL": "CONTRACTUAL SCHEDULE",
