    "Nous gérons les démarches<br class=\"hidden xl:block\"> administratives locales (permis,<br class=\"hidden xl:block\"> raccordements) pour vous.": "We handle local administrative<br class=\"hidden xl:block\"> procedures (permits,<br class=\"hidden xl:block\"> connections) for you.",
